## Key Features Implemented

| Feature | Implementation |
|---------|---------------|
| Dynamic concurrency | `RateLimiter` halves on 429/403/5xx, recovers +1 on success |
| Exponential backoff | Decorator with jitter, configurable max retries |
| Resume policy | Retry `rate_limited`/`error`; skip `ok` unless `--refresh-ok` |
| Content hashing | SHA-256 truncated to 16 chars for change detection |
| Strict validation | 11-char `video_id`, `UC`-prefix `channel_id`, datetime |
| Discovery caching | `data/discovery_cache.json` persists API results |
| CLI flags | `--dry-run`, `--limit`, `--since`, `--refresh-ok`, `--compact` |

